<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta name="viewpoint" content="width=device-width, initial-scalre= 1">
  <meta http-equiv="Cache-control" content="public">
  <title>Upload file</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-WskhaSGFgHYWDcbwN70/dfYBj47jz9qbsMId/iRN3ewGhXQFZCSftd1LZCfmhktB" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <!-- <script type ="text/javascript" src="dbFunctions.js" >  </script> -->
</head>

<body>
  <% include ../fixed/nav %>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class = "col-md-auto" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">
        <p class= "border border-info rounded p-3">
        <span class="text-info"> Only csv file is accepted </span>
        The each row of the file should follow the format below:
        country, option, spelling, spelling ,...

        Options are: "a" for alternative spelling for country.
                     "m" for misspelling for country.
                     "ac" for alternative spelling for capital.
                     "mc" for misspelling for capital.

                     options with "a" are 5 point spellings and "m" are 3 point spellings.

        example:
        Algeria, m, Algear
        Algeria, mc, Algers, Aleris

        All of these records will be appened to the list in the database and will skip any
        duplicates. If you wish to update country or capital name or do further editing,
        please go to edit country page.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4 mt-5">
    <form class="form-group" method="POST" action="/fileUpload" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <div class="form-group">
            <label>Upload File: </label>
             <input type="file" name ="file" class="form-control"/>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group mt-3">
            <input type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-info"/>
       </div>
     </form>
   </div>
   </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
